item.title: A Bad Day for Democrats -- and Terrorists
item.description: Gateway Pundit provides this top-shelf story of a US F-16 taking out 30 or so al Qaeda terrorists in Iraq. It’s a thing of beauty, and it must make Democrats sick to see their well-trained comrades die under American attack.
